| customerID (PK)    |      | rentalID (PK)     |       | movieID (PK)     |
| name               |      | rentDate          |       | title            |
| email              |<-----| returnDate        |       | genre            |
| phone              |      | rentalStatus      |       | director         |
+--------------------+      | customerID (FK)   |       | cast             |
